CSS Selectors

Tag name - p { color: green; }

Class name - .coffeeType { color: green; }

Element ID - #siteHeader { color: green; }

Combined selector - p.coffeeType { color: yellow; }

Child selectors -
.coffeetype a { color: red; }
.coffeetype > a { color: red; }

Pseudo classes - 
a:link { color: blue; }
a:visited { color: red; }
a:hover {color : green;}
a:active { color: red; }

Pseudo elements - p:first-child { color: red; }
